==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Unce
<hw>Unce</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[L. <ets>uncia</ets> ounce. See
<er>Ounce</er> a weight.]</ety> <def>An ounce; a small portion.</def>
<mark>[Obs.]</mark> ⟦ldquo⟧By <xex>unces</xex> hung his locks.⟦rdquo⟧
<rj><au>Chaucer.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

